title: Christmas.The.Bob.Newhart.Show.Holiday.Episodes.s1-4
description:
This download includes the following holiday themed episodes from

The Bob Newhart Show (1972-1978).


Season 1. His Busiest Season (12/23/72)

Season 2. I'm Dreaming of a Slight Christmas (12/22/73)

Season 3. Home is Where the Hurt Is (12/21/74)

Season 4. Bob Has to Have His Tonsils Out, So He Spends Christmas Eve in the Hospital (12/20/75)



There were also Christmas themed episodes in seasons 5-6 but, to my knowledge, 
the last two seasons were never released to video. :(

Season 5. Making Up is the Thing to Do (12/25/76)

Season 6. Twas the Pie Before Christmas (12/24/77)
